## When to run
- After every edit batch: typecheck + lint (fast gates)
- Before every commit: all blocking gates
- Before PR / merge / deploy: the full table

## Failure protocol
- A failing gate BLOCKS the commit — fix forward or revert; never bypass (no `--no-verify`, no skipped CI)
- Report the exact command + exit code — "should work" is not a verification
- Flaky test: quarantine with a DECISIONS.md entry — never delete to go green

## Content policy
- Zero placeholder content (lorem, TODO copy, stub assets) in any shipped surface

## Division of labor
- The verifier agent runs this table mechanically; this rule binds the main thread to the same gates
